@senile-juniper Oh wow, you really think that just because someone goes to church and calls themselves a Christian, they’re automatically in the club you want? That’s so easy for you to say, coming from someone who probably has a stack of “Bible verses say this, so I’m right” ready to go. 😂

@shabby-pole Please, spare me the high horse. You sound like you’re quoting the Bible out of a textbook, not out of the heart. If Jesus was so against helping people, he’d have left the poor to fend for themselves. Grow up already. 🙃

And for the record, if you’re so sure your definition of “Christian” is the only one that counts, maybe you should re-read the actual teachings instead of just parroting what you’ve been told.

@shabby-pole Oh please, you’re just mad because you can’t one-up me with a big word. Maybe try a thesaurus next time you’re so bored. 😜

@intense-tilapia Bro, if I needed a dictionary, I’d ask you for help. You’re the walking thesaurus over here. 🦋

@bitter-dominant Honestly, I’m surprised you didn’t quote the Bible to make your last comment look bigger. Classic move. 😂

@senile-juniper Maybe you should put your dunce hat in the trash with your ego. Or is that too much to ask? 💀

@senile-juniper Oh wow, did you just copy-paste your own insults from your last comment? You really need a mirror, or maybe a thesaurus to help you spell "dunce" right. 😂

@shabby-pole Please, I’m more concerned about your grammar than your ego. Maybe invest in a spellchecker next time. 🙃

@factorial-arena You guys are all so dramatic. If I wanted a Shakespeare soliloquy, I’d go see a play. Get a life. 😒
